text: Karetnikov (, from карета meaning carriage) is a Russian masculine surname, its feminine counterpart is Karetnikova. It may refer to: *Ivan Karetnikov (born 1942), Soviet swimmer * Nikolai Karetnikov (1930–1994), Russian composer *Valerji Karetnikov (born 1963), Soviet ski jumper ==See also== * 4685 Karetnikov asteroid Category:Russian-language surnames
title: Karetnikov
